import torch
import torch.nn as nn
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
import json, os, pathlib

from dataset import Spec, fit_encoders, TabularDS, collate
from models import TabularConfig, TabularClassifier, nn as _nn
from callbacks import MetricLogger, EarlyStopping, ModelCheckpoint, LRSchedulerCallback, History
from trainer import Trainer, eval_and_plot_confusion
from utils import quick_compare

print(torch.cuda.is_available())
device=torch.device('cuda' if torch.cuda.is_available() else 'cpu')

cache = f"/tmp/torchinductor_{os.getuid()}"
os.environ["TORCHINDUCTOR_CACHE_DIR"] = cache
pathlib.Path(cache).mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)

torch.backends.cuda.matmul.allow_tf32 = True
torch.backends.cudnn.allow_tf32 = True
torch.set_float32_matmul_precision("high")

True
In[2]:
df = pd.read_csv('processed.csv')
spec = Spec(
    num_cols=['Age', 'ALB', 'ALT', 'BIL', 'CHE', 'CHOL', 'CREA', 'GGT', 'PROT'],
    cat_cols=['is_male'],
    target_col='class',
    drop_cols=['Unnamed: 0', 'Sex', 'Category', 'Category_norm']
)

y = df['class'].to_numpy()
idx = np.arange(len(df))
idx_tr, idx_tmp, y_tr, y_tmp = train_test_split(idx, y, test_size=0.2, stratify=y, random_state=42)
idx_va, idx_te, y_va, t_te = train_test_split(idx_tmp, y_tmp, test_size=0.5, stratify=y_tmp, random_state=42)

enc = fit_encoders(df.iloc[idx_tr], spec)
num_workers = max(4, (os.cpu_count() or 8)//2)

ds_tr = TabularDS(df.iloc[idx_tr], spec, enc)
ds_va = TabularDS(df.iloc[idx_va], spec, enc)
ds_te = TabularDS(df.iloc[idx_te], spec, enc)

bs = len(ds_tr)
dl_tr = torch.utils.data.DataLoader(ds_tr, batch_size=bs, shuffle=True, collate_fn=collate, num_workers=num_workers,
    pin_memory=True, persistent_workers=True)
dl_va = torch.utils.data.DataLoader(ds_va, batch_size=bs, shuffle=False, collate_fn=collate, num_workers=num_workers,
    pin_memory=True, persistent_workers=True)
dl_te = torch.utils.data.DataLoader(ds_te, batch_size=bs, shuffle=False, collate_fn=collate, num_workers=num_workers,
    pin_memory=True, persistent_workers=True)
In[3]:
cat_cardinalities = [len(enc.cat_maps[c]) + 1 for c in spec.cat_cols] # + 1 for UNK

neg = (y_tr == 0).sum()
pos = (y_tr == 1).sum()
pos_weight = torch.tensor(neg / pos, dtype=torch.float32)

pos_weight.item()

In[4]:
cfg_model = TabularConfig(
    d_num = ds_tr.x_num.shape[1],
    cat_cardinalities=cat_cardinalities,
    emb_dims=3,
    hidden = [1024,2048,1024],
    activation = 'ReLU',
    dropout = 0,
    use_batchnorm=False,
    output_dim=1
)

big_model = TabularClassifier(cfg_model)

opt = torch.optim.AdamW(big_model.parameters(), lr=1e-3, weight_decay=0,fused=torch.cuda.is_available())
crit = nn.BCEWithLogitsLoss(pos_weight=None)
sched = torch.optim.lr_scheduler.CosineAnnealingLR(opt, T_max=30)

cbs = [
    MetricLogger(log_every_n_steps=50),
    ModelCheckpoint(dirpath='checkpoints', filename='model_big',
        monitor='val_loss', mode='min', save_best_only=True, save_last=True),
    LRSchedulerCallback(scheduler=sched, step_on='epoch'),
]

hist = History()
cbs.append(hist)
In[]:
trainer = Trainer(big_model, opt, crit, scheduler=sched, callbacks=cbs, cfg=None, device=device, compile_model=True)
trainer.fit(dl_tr, dl_va, epochs=250)
In[6]:
df_hist = hist.to_frame()
df_hist.to_csv('metrics_history.csv', index=False)

plt.figure(); df_hist["val_auprc"].plot(); plt.title("Val AUPRC"); plt.xlabel("epoch"); plt.ylabel("AUPRC")

plt.figure(); df_hist[["train_loss","val_loss"]].plot(); plt.title("Loss"); plt.xlabel("epoch"); plt.ylabel("loss"); plt.ylim(0,0.6)
plt.show()

In[9]:
cfg_model = TabularConfig(
    d_num = ds_tr.x_num.shape[1],
    cat_cardinalities=cat_cardinalities,
    emb_dims=3,
    hidden = [1024,2048,1024],
    activation = 'ReLU',
    dropout = 0.2,
    use_batchnorm=False,
    output_dim=1
)

big_model_reg = TabularClassifier(cfg_model)

opt = torch.optim.AdamW(big_model_reg.parameters(), lr=1e-3, weight_decay=2.5e-2,fused=torch.cuda.is_available())
crit = nn.BCEWithLogitsLoss(pos_weight=None)
sched = torch.optim.lr_scheduler.CosineAnnealingLR(opt, T_max=30)

cbs = [
    MetricLogger(log_every_n_steps=50),
    ModelCheckpoint(dirpath='checkpoints', filename='model_big_prevent',
        monitor='val_loss', mode='min', save_best_only=True, save_last=True),
    EarlyStopping(metric='val_loss', mode='min', patience=50),
    LRSchedulerCallback(scheduler=sched, step_on='epoch'),
]

hist = History()
cbs.append(hist)
In[]:
trainer = Trainer(big_model_reg, opt, crit, scheduler=sched, callbacks=cbs, cfg=None, device=device, compile_model=True)
trainer.fit(dl_tr, dl_va, epochs=250)
